
# RecycLens – AI-Powered Waste Sorting Tool

**Author:** Chiamaka Ekene  
**Last Updated:** 21/11/2025  
**Status:** Draft MVP  

RecycLens is a lightweight AI-powered prototype that helps urban residents in Nigeria and Ghana quickly identify and sort household waste. Using image recognition, the app provides simple, actionable disposal guidance to improve recycling habits, reduce confusion, and encourage environmentally responsible behavior.

